languages.text: "Судя по тому, что местные обитатели чуть тебя не прикончили, что-то пошло не по плану".
"Seeing as the inhabitants of this place almost killed you, I gather that something went wrong with this plan of yours."
languages.original_text: "Судя по тому, что местные обитатели чуть тебя не прикончили, что-то пошло не по плану".

traits.locale_text: "It seems that something didn't go as planned, seeing as the local inhabitants tried to finish you off."
"It seems that something didn't go as planned, seeing as the local inhabitants tried to finish you off."
"It seems like something went sideways, seeing as the locals were about to croak you."
"It seems like something went sideways, seeing as the locals were about to croak you."

"Seeing as the inhabitants of this place almost killed you, I gather that something went wrong with this plan of yours."

languages.text: « Étant donné que les habitants de cette planète ont failli vous tuer, j'en déduis que votre plan a mal tourné. »
languages.original_text: "Seeing as the inhabitants of this place almost killed you, I gather that something went wrong with this plan of yours."

traits.locale_text: « Étant donné que les habitants de cette planète ont failli vous tuer, j'en déduis que votre plan a mal tourné. »

languages.text: «Dado que los habitantes de este lugar casi le matan, entiendo que algo falló en su plan».
languages.original_text: "Seeing as the inhabitants of this place almost killed you, I gather that something went wrong with this plan of yours."

traits.locale_text: «Parece que algo no fue según lo previsto, porque los habitantes estaban a punto de poner fin a todo esto».

languages.text: “不过，住在这里的当地人差点就把你干掉了，我猜你的计划怕是出了点岔子。”
languages.original_text: "Seeing as the inhabitants of this place almost killed you, I gather that something went wrong with this plan of yours."

traits.locale_text: “不过，看起来计划好像出了问题，因为这里的当地人打算把你干掉。”

languages.text: "Angesichts der Tatsache, dass die Einheimischen Euch fast getötet hätten, ist Euer Plan wohl schiefgegangen."
languages.original_text: "Seeing as the inhabitants of this place almost killed you, I gather that something went wrong with this plan of yours."

traits.locale_text: "Irgendwas ist offenbar schiefgegangen, wenn die Einheimischen Euch töten wollen."

languages.text: 「現地の住民がお前を殺そうとしたことから、その計画は何かがうまくいかなかったようだな」
languages.original_text: "Seeing as the inhabitants of this place almost killed you, I gather that something went wrong with this plan of yours."

traits.locale_text: 「現地の住民がお前を殺そうとしたのを見ると、何かがうまくいかなかったようだな」

languages.text: "Buranın sakinleri seni neredeyse öldürdüğüne göre planında yolunda gitmeyen bir şeyler olmuş."
languages.original_text: "Seeing as the inhabitants of this place almost killed you, I gather that something went wrong with this plan of yours."
